you were never really here is a 2017 british-french-american thriller film written and directed by lynne ramsay , based on the novella of the same name by jonathan ames .   the film stars joaquin phoenix , ekaterina samsonov , alex manette , john doman and judith roberts .   it premiered at the 70th cannes film festival in the main competition section , where lynne ramsay won the best screenplay award and joaquin phoenix won the award for best actor .